@startuml
title Feature 026. Admin RBAC and internal accounts sequence

actor "Суперадмин" as SuperAdmin
actor "Администратор безопасности" as SecurityAdmin
actor "HR/операционный администратор" as HrAdmin
actor "Аудитор" as Auditor
participant "Frontend /admin/rbac" as Frontend
participant "Auth module" as Auth
participant "admin-rbac controller" as Controller
participant "admin-rbac service" as Service
participant "admin-rbac security policy" as Policy
database "admin-rbac DB" as Db
participant "Audit publisher" as Audit
participant "Integration client" as Integration

== Создание и выдача доступа ==
SuperAdmin -> Frontend: Открывает /admin/rbac
Frontend -> Auth: GET current session
Auth --> Frontend: roles, permission matrix, elevated state
Frontend -> Controller: POST /api/admin/rbac/accounts
Controller -> Policy: Проверить role, permission set, scope, elevated session
Policy --> Controller: allowed
Controller -> Service: createInternalAccount(request, correlationId)
Service -> Db: insert internal_account
Service -> Audit: ADMIN_ACCOUNT_CREATED(actor, target, diff)
Audit -> Db: insert audit_event
Service --> Controller: InternalAccountResponse
Controller --> Frontend: 201 account without secrets

Frontend -> Controller: POST /accounts/{id}/permission-preview
Controller -> Policy: Проверить scope preview
Controller -> Service: calculateEffectivePermissions(request)
Service -> Db: read roles, permission sets, scopes
Service --> Controller: effectivePermissions, conflicts, requiredMfa
Controller --> Frontend: 200 preview

SuperAdmin -> Frontend: Подтверждает роли и scopes
Frontend -> Controller: PUT /accounts/{id}/roles + X-Elevated-Session-Id
Controller -> Policy: Проверить elevated/MFA и отсутствие конфликтов
Policy --> Controller: allowed
Controller -> Service: replaceAccountAccess(request)
Service -> Db: upsert account_role and responsibility_scope
Service -> Audit: ADMIN_ROLE_ASSIGNED / ADMIN_PERMISSION_SET_CHANGED
Audit -> Db: insert audit_event
Controller --> Frontend: 200 updated effective permission matrix

== Запрет вне scope ==
HrAdmin -> Frontend: Пытается выдать admin permission set
Frontend -> Controller: PUT /accounts/{id}/roles
Controller -> Policy: Проверить responsibility scope
Policy --> Controller: denied STR_MNEMO_ADMIN_RBAC_SCOPE_DENIED
Controller --> Frontend: 403 ErrorResponse
Controller -> Audit: access denied event

== Security policy и service account ==
SecurityAdmin -> Frontend: Обновляет MFA/session policy
Frontend -> Controller: PUT /security-policies + X-Elevated-Session-Id
Controller -> Policy: Проверить elevated session
Controller -> Service: updateSecurityPolicy(request)
Service -> Db: update security_policy version
Service -> Audit: ADMIN_POLICY_CHANGED
Controller --> Frontend: 200 SecurityPolicyResponse

SecurityAdmin -> Frontend: Ротирует service account WMS
Frontend -> Controller: POST /service-accounts/{id}/rotate-secret
Controller -> Policy: Проверить SECURITY_ADMIN и elevated session
Controller -> Service: rotateServiceAccountSecret(id)
Service -> Db: mark previous secret EXPIRING
Service -> Db: insert new secret hash and masked hint
Service -> Audit: ADMIN_SERVICE_ACCOUNT_ROTATED
Controller --> Frontend: 200 oneTimeSecret
Frontend --> SecurityAdmin: Показывает secret один раз

Integration -> Controller: API request with service credentials
Controller -> Service: validateServiceAccountCredential()
Service -> Db: read service account status and active secret
Service --> Controller: scopes or disabled

== Emergency deactivation и audit ==
SuperAdmin -> Frontend: Запускает emergency deactivation
Frontend -> Controller: POST /emergency-deactivations + X-Elevated-Session-Id
Controller -> Policy: Проверить critical elevated action
Controller -> Service: emergencyDeactivate(target)
Service -> Db: deactivate account/role/permission_set
Service -> Auth: terminate affected sessions
Service -> Audit: ADMIN_EMERGENCY_DEACTIVATED
Controller --> Frontend: 204

Auditor -> Frontend: Ищет audit trail
Frontend -> Controller: GET /audit-events?targetUserId=&actionCode=
Controller -> Policy: Проверить audit permission
Controller -> Service: searchAuditEvents(filter)
Service -> Db: select immutable audit events
Service --> Controller: AuditEventListResponse without secrets
Controller --> Frontend: 200 audit events

@enduml
